ch.nolix.core.documentNode

Class Statement

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.nolix.core.documentNode.Statement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Headered

    public final class Statement
extends java.lang.Object
implements Headered
    A Statement consists of a DocumentNode and optionally a next Statement. A Statement is not mutable as long as its document node or next statement are not mutated.
    Author:
    Silvan Wyss
